    "rendered": "\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-9d6595d7 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full is-resized\"><a href=\"https://i0.wp.com/kriskrug.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/krug-1.webp?ssl=1\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"780\" height=\"712\" data-attachment-id=\"5113\" data-permalink=\"https://kriskrug.co/podcast-guesting-page-epk/krug-1-2/#main\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/kriskrug.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/krug-1.webp?fit=1024%2C935&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"1024,935\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"krug-1\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/kriskrug.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/krug-1.webp?fit=780%2C712&amp;ssl=1\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/kriskrug.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/krug-1.webp?resize=780%2C712&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-5113\" style=\"width:375px;height:auto\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/kriskrug.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/krug-1.webp?w=1024&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/kriskrug.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/krug-1.webp?resize=300%2C274&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/kriskrug.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/krug-1.webp?resize=768%2C701&amp;ssl=1 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 780px) 100vw, 780px\" /></a></figure>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\">\n<p></p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\">My name is Kris Krug – a boundary-pushing Creative Explorer, an intuitive Tech Whisperer, and a tenacious Culture Hacker. In the fabric of the digital era, where technology often overshadows humanity, I&#8217;ve taken it upon myself to chart a different course. I’m on a relentless mission to humanize technology, to infuse it with empathy, ethics, and emotion. I&#8217;m not just tinkering with gadgets and algorithms; I&#8217;m reprogramming the very core of our interactions with the digital world to resonate with the heartbeat of human experience.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-align-center\"><strong>Recent podcast</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns alignwide is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-9d6595d7 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-center is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n<span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"780\" height=\"439\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/pss7CfiiBxg?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span>\n</div></figure>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-center is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed alignfull is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n<span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"780\" height=\"439\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/wJUKAmwRHS4?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span>\n</div></figure>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-center is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed alignfull is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n<span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"780\" height=\"439\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/SMg_RLx_2Q4?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span>\n</div></figure>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns alignwide is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-9d6595d7 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed alignfull is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n<span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"780\" height=\"439\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/DfImC9WTvgA?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span>\n</div></figure>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\"><div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-large is-resized\"><a href=\"https://www.buzzsprout.com/2277759/14785748\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"780\" height=\"780\" data-attachment-id=\"5273\" data-permalink=\"https://kriskrug.co/podcast-guesting-page-epk/the20upgrade20-20beyond20the20hype20-20podcast20artwork/#main\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/kriskrug.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/The20Upgrade20-20Beyond20The20Hype20-20Podcast20Artwork.jpg?fit=1400%2C1400&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"1400,1400\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"The20Upgrade20-20Beyond20The20Hype20-20Podcast20Artwork\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/kriskrug.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/The20Upgrade20-20Beyond20The20Hype20-20Podcast20Artwork.jpg?fit=780%2C780&amp;ssl=1\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/kriskrug.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/The20Upgrade20-20Beyond20The20Hype20-20Podcast20Artwork.jpg?resize=780%2C780&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-5273\" style=\"width:310px;height:auto\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/kriskrug.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/The20Upgrade20-20Beyond20The20Hype20-20Podcast20Artwork.jpg?resize=1024%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/kriskrug.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/The20Upgrade20-20Beyond20The20Hype20-20Podcast20Artwork.jpg?resize=300%2C300&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/kriskrug.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/The20Upgrade20-20Beyond20The20Hype20-20Podcast20Artwork.jpg?resize=150%2C150&amp;ssl=1 150w, https://i0.wp.com/kriskrug.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/The20Upgrade20-20Beyond20The20Hype20-20Podcast20Artwork.jpg?resize=768%2C768&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/kriskrug.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/The20Upgrade20-20Beyond20The20Hype20-20Podcast20Artwork.jpg?resize=200%2C200&amp;ssl=1 200w, https://i0.wp.com/kriskrug.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/The20Upgrade20-20Beyond20The20Hype20-20Podcast20Artwork.jpg?resize=100%2C100&amp;ssl=1 100w, https://i0.wp.com/kriskrug.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/The20Upgrade20-20Beyond20The20Hype20-20Podcast20Artwork.jpg?resize=40%2C40&amp;ssl=1 40w, https://i0.wp.com/kriskrug.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/The20Upgrade20-20Beyond20The20Hype20-20Podcast20Artwork.jpg?w=1400&amp;ssl=1 1400w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 780px) 100vw, 780px\" /></a></figure>\n</div></div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed alignfull is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n<span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"780\" height=\"439\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/UUQzgOZhqc0?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span>\n</div></figure>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n\n\n\n<iframe loading=\"lazy\" height=\"200px\" width=\"100%\" frameborder=\"no\" scrolling=\"no\" seamless src=\"https://player.simplecast.com/73cda8b0-9364-4068-b91a-0e6c4f0f6bad?dark=true\"></iframe>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>I&#8217;d Like to Be You Next Podcast Guest</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Looking for a guest who embodies the intersection of art, technology, and community? Meet Kris Krüg, an accomplished photographer, fervent open-source advocate, and pioneering digital strategist based in Vancouver.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Why Kris Stands Out:</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><strong>TED Talks Photographer</strong>: Captured iconic figures like Bill Clinton, Barack Obama, Richard Branson, and more. His eye for storytelling through visuals is unparalleled.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>130,000+ Creative Commons Photos</strong>: His robust photography archive is a community asset that fuels both nonprofit initiatives and his own commercial projects.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Digital Pioneer</strong>: With a finger on the pulse of emerging tech trends, Kris navigates the evolving landscape of digital marketing, focusing on human-centric approaches.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Core Philosophies:</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><strong>Openness</strong>: A stalwart advocate for open-source technologies and transparent communication, Kris believes in the power of shared knowledge and collective problem-solving.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Marketing</strong>: Kris eschews the traditional numbers game in favor of a more compassionate, adaptive digital strategy.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Community</strong>: He’s not just talking about community; he’s building it—through grassroots projects that foster meaningful connections.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Personal Branding</strong>: Authenticity is at the heart of Kris&#8217;s brand, a multidimensional reflection of his skills in photography, tech, and community engagement.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Interdisciplinary Expertise</strong>: Where art meets tech, you&#8217;ll find Kris—seamlessly transitioning between multiple roles and demonstrating how creativity enhances innovation.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Your audience will walk away not just informed, but inspired and equipped with actionable insights they can implement in their own lives.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Links to Explore:</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><a href=\"https://chat.openai.com/c/d8c5e4ff-bc38-4dcd-8c2e-ecaab78ffff2#\">Blog</a></li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https://chat.openai.com/c/d8c5e4ff-bc38-4dcd-8c2e-ecaab78ffff2#\">YouTube</a></li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https://chat.openai.com/c/d8c5e4ff-bc38-4dcd-8c2e-ecaab78ffff2#\">Facebook</a></li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https://chat.openai.com/c/d8c5e4ff-bc38-4dcd-8c2e-ecaab78ffff2#\">Flickr</a></li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https://chat.openai.com/c/d8c5e4ff-bc38-4dcd-8c2e-ecaab78ffff2#\">LinkedIn</a></li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Contact Kris to explore collaboration opportunities and to make your next podcast episode a captivating experience your audience won’t forget.</p>\n",
